skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: green score
des:
The skill is designed to help everyone get "greenscore's"(i.e, walk and bike scores) of their cities and random facts based on the score for their city to conserve energy and promote green environment. The score identifies if a city is walk-able, car-dependant and/or bike-able city and provides random fact/ideas based on green score of a city. 

Adapting to some of the ideas can have a huge impact and lead to more environmental friendly living. Small changes, each day, can help protect Earth and create a beautiful home for our future generations!

Scores powered by Walk Score® https://www.walkscore.com/"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
